---
description: Specs: keep them compact, non-duplicative, MUST/MUST NOT, Cursor-friendly
globs:
  - "specs/**/*.md"
alwaysApply: false
---

- Each spec must include: ID, VERSION, STATUS, APPLIES_TO.
- Use concise MUST/MUST NOT statements; avoid duplicated content across specs.
- Put examples (user-facing) in Dutch; everything else in English.
- If adding a new requirement, link it from NFR-00 and/or SP-00 instead of repeating it.
